isk note by removing the suggestion to lower aggressiveness because it referenced poor performance. The broader risk thesis might still stand, even with a current return of 15.44. But the statement \"模拟盘状态差\" seems inaccurate. The risk warning was based on walk-forward and market conditions, not just current profit. I'll clarify these points in my response and update only the relevant lines.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_0fad9e409c19087f0169e3402d0574819a980248bc01dbb034\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp40A2txJ6A4i5CNcO4SmBT55eMt3AIhXKW8xf6rQmO-FvNYkr5po3iarHgDZ1HeEk318ROIPXfdIuWzrbR5zG2P-B41etQeNVTva8CkcDJAWOTi4ApxWNWxyVIT2Ic4oBxXjcYtFq7LjMMjwqTFt1scnj7huN6yK8uPusdG9UG_MsNsLrxSZjIf508TMTS3zCKto2_fzY-MMY2T2YdowrTBKsPZMLpFWGtT2s88zFgzTL0HC54dzJNsoKM3k5D38eeG8yOh7_8orZhcgMYRh5y7sGsmCZyW2O4eHSd-6yd52r856D519VUJVo2KETPO-f_UwAFyxTiTT2gz0ji_euOL17EBItBdOxjPYQ9beuWcF8b0puq8AffyDgmaMKX3h4dol4Ms3vfYiEYoQUkBKSYcIeOGkVPiQmVk7uMlvjSUyLuW9YQDMlZ5nro15xsqKrVPZVUQpaG_3l2BxY-jMQLNeMJPFHXsZR5E1JsEnRhstQ589jzMD5ocI1WwocBwSf4JqheeioCAGpGfLdswiIYx-sHcLvol9NwmO0jNhytg2Qo-5ec2_31Bq7lMS5_w0nAQc55d0HlVLnHoLXrC8ffM6CBw7rPEeyeNY6--Rda9qVChonu2GYh_Xt0xEU-Fyc515k9gKyCMThD5HyTrLPLmwiW94xzpIwLqNgmMKCzlwwCitGGh_kFtzuj8_xkW-pCaNWkmCUhv4kC2Jqe-1JSyirm5USyYubM86zkIYdrNid_U0ZTQAvsdxoMpiGa9nlurJmjotlJK7G3NDjXxCrHI-QFPsmnI3a641TAtn0N3iMrduAwkaD14E8gUKN5GzFWl4VfucrQEvV7aOezlzGBNhinwxgbE3TqFq8vHjtoLduMARBmwxO2QypEZHtbzBvLKmIkHYjPfWRowAkyXtrREdsURQhYlxrV_WQYOuVJhwoV1W-YmbbrVSaLqxGIZUpRY1x59aTFdENVDIvnGnmKv44ae_weCb8HANlwDuX3DmhQnfTUWiFgk_ft-WDInDWoA4auc1N2eZR1Jo-g22h7-DqY3P4oVX41UK7P6iJab0BwkXURsGxyqkOcTna1-SlAHHCqk_2WAfjdXwiTi1eCgubzxRKL6hjk9CwrJGVho6vNWDHNWB3QRwt11jHnX4KBYpHzTjpzsB_XSzDQQeFt5Kmo1OGrka3XUphAuFGKqRjZvmKlBpOKV7ve1LdjGzYdwAtxYk2YZIPkS2_9UkQRBvgugkIWRnWjsQ62q53JCq9x-z8Cn_oYowIUmbzMP3fxw1_RuuZx9Ax7pEanekKMZHnifnE7VFR6ms8-9BF0DwFATbeNpbcxU061kzmxF0UByc3habdBt2xy0IEXVunPlyJTVl4JofbrcGy0XxDeIuLaPxAopztFxVXpuIVGYWaAwW5c54vsn2DfKdhZNpAKJkNVv8bR4RLwUHdyzkMEfgWL6nnlFxyyq