级：动作建议**  \n     只有当前两级都时间对齐，才给“减仓/报警/推送飞书”\n\n一句话：  \n**这个风险快照对你还有用，但更适合做“研究雷达”，不适合直接做“交易扳机”。**\n\n如果你愿意，我可以下一步直接把它改成一个**不会再串口径的三层风险快照模板**。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0fad9e409c19087f0169e34ef714c4819aa612cab806ff29a1\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"beecode","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":69613,"output":786,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":70399,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776504556260,"responseId":"resp_0fad9e409c19087f0169e34eeddea0819abce02082d5b0d124"}}
