t7TaUJW9i06_ku_04rWG6sauMF0aLCt5XCfTGfpXmpNG_l4RMOfIaNVmCByBy5cZSAI0zpmpvCp_11YHv8cFrCNVPDASbdBt5iIoj1wgJvKgxnTkCZ3iguRcom8imMz5Did_u6F_gLYOhxFfCKj4VHvfjXYw_H2T0slWMP2p_lI2veh21wcG7UN1Fd4JpJKo45YU5JJXso7FxFTfNWXLYMrb_-eNvMFjEoqK63WAaMHNS5ZpTln2RIntnhkJj3a3UjkpOOEU0FnJIB0OQPiYwdhebiuxaZ6fgegPG6ckrxAMdWk66fF_oDHdtfteFjmIf8y-TEMFMvRnl9_YzGJfL1DcBxvUN2yVM38Z4QJaRhewmuejqzBUnWPUX9NMZtoygy4xONoatLJ5J1F8N8FlSGRx21KD4zvdRNWNbiDJLDz8Um_A72qgsWzi_VmI9Sjkg683zOcYfQyLa2wNBCt7f7Hn4dQ0d73Mgdf7qll0QCiKKPDYPvLiTnV0SMf6irOEdEjhAid-2JOxMMUIxjEoRMYd8vZGa29XDoCB6oV3SXbeC2vXBYZ9gh5wsHPd5EkLYlCCbiG4xqC3xYDSOaMBpJileEp8UwOc8uFGo65tbvVmravVHjX5DJ0otsNC0ZEJFJETV1kTrVdaKciA-vr1YbCUh50ghjH7qfw9ui845rz2CejHPh0XQheko_LML-9cG7bU4-ZK9-070LxWyY7c9vE43_1dIGfBdutkJw_4SSijiTDRFfr240pKoJTgtyENOn5R3xffWbhac_vAw7fZxMpharfG9CuV1gVEQSYlKCc2csdCQ1bAih9PLy4vzOpbLjEns6468pnVVQzpa_oCcYFQI-bHp3HwtwPAQQmJYog3iiWxK2wMS3JywGkBM20tSkQKWSTcOfytUvIb7PuX6Tg6xME1rR5_vxHAnDcNPZ4NANAjeky9v84X0Ku3_t1LmoYP_2yVqcfZQWMdExRnJ4aVScu8SypIjKTx6iS9nBpi0nEVuqACVvnTro23R8ZIsXkuDVZH6NvTXENCssd2U8g5OhL4Y53hSGXDYJXsXTF69Ry0kt9o1m1p3FwP1untT0DUuBCNY2CVpFsIJxqAzedVwSdE5FXHnkjTPB0J_4OS8g_C0_mlPU7_V0np66Zr6q2eiuiRf9vX7hnfZSbCwHl9hE4hvnqlRRvmZINzwU9pBkGzZC-z54j5-TPb9EzY3RaK683E9OjHMqTEw==\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Clarifying report structure**\\n\\nI need to separate the content into two parts: one is the simulation snapshot derived from the nav curve, and the other is the latest account snapshot from the JSON file reflecting the current account health. The task instructions emphasize distinguishing between the Layer 2 account snapshot and the analysis window, possibly highlighting discrepancies in freshness with a \\\"red flag.\\\" It seems I might need to modify the current report template to accommodate a three-layer format for clarity.\"},{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Considering function design**\\n\\nI’m thinking about creating a helper function called `fmt_pct` that formats percentages nicely. It should return a question mark if the input value is `None` and format numerical values to two decimal places with a percent sign. Hm, I wonder if I should make a similar function for Sharpe ratios, but it might not be necessary. Maybe I should ensure that this helper is robust for older values and consider using global functions instead.\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"我会顺手给当前这份 4/18 报告补个“仅限研究快照、不可直接当交易警报”的醒目标注，避免你后面翻旧报告又踩一次坑。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0fad9e409c19087f0169e350084ed4819abeb061d768ed941c\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_XfhfmmSwLl3w6ivPu5PyNdWE|fc_0fad9e409c19087f0169e350091f48819a89d5c13390568bdb","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/run_strategy_hypothesis_weekly.py","edits":[{"oldText":"def load_paper_nav_csv(profile_slug: str) -> dict | None:\n    csv_path = REPORT_DIR / f\"paper_{profile_slug}_nav_curve_v1.csv\"\n    if not csv_path.exists():\n        return None\n    try:\n        import pandas as pd\n        df = pd.read_csv(csv_path)\n        if \"date\" not in df.columns and \"trade_date\" not in df.columns:\n            return None\n        date_col = \"date\" if \"date\" in df.columns else \"trade_date\"\n        df[date_col] = pd.to_datetime(df[date_col], errors=\"coerce\")\n        df = df.dropna(subset=[date_col]).sort_values(date_col)\n        if len(df) < 2:\n            return None\n        # NAV 从 initial_cash（1000000.0）开始，计算相对收益率\n        initial_nav = float(df.iloc[0][\"nav\"]) if \"nav\" in df.columns else 1000000.0\n        today = datetime.now()\n        week_ago = today - pd.Timedelta(days=7)\n        df_week = df[df[date_col] >= week_ago]\n        last_row = df.iloc[-1]\n        last_nav = float(last_row.get(\"nav\", initial_nav))\n        first_week_row = df_week.iloc[0] if len(df_week) > 0 else df.iloc[0]\n        first_nav = float(first_week_row.get(\"nav\", initial_nav))\n        total_return = (last_nav / initial_nav - 1.0) * 100\n        week_return = (last_nav / first_nav - 1.0) * 100 if len(df_week) > 0 else 0.0\n        return {\n            \"latest_nav\": last_nav,\n            \"initial_nav\": initial_nav,\n            \"total_return_pct\": total_return,\n            \"week_return_pct\": week_return,\n            \"latest_date\": str(last_row.get(date_col, \"\"))[:10],\n            \"data_points\": len(df),\n        }\n    except Exception:\n        return None\n\n\ndef load_cb_market_data() -> dict:\n","newText":"def load_paper_nav_csv(profile_slug: str) -> dict | None:\n    csv_path = REPORT_DIR / f\"paper_{profile_slug}_nav_curve_v1.csv\"\n    if not csv_path.exists():\n        return None\n    try:\n        import pandas as pd\n        df = pd.read_csv(csv_path)\n        if \"date\" not in df.columns and \"trade_date\" not in df.columns:\n            return None\n        date_col = \"date\" if \"date\" in df.columns else \"trade_date\"\n        df[date_col] = pd.to_datetime(df[date_col], errors=\"coerce\")\n        df = df.dropna(subset=[date_col]).sort_values(date_col)\n        if len(df) < 2:\n            return None\n        # NAV 从 initial_cash（1000000.0）开始，计算相对收益率\n        initial_nav = float(df.iloc[0][\"nav\"]) if \"nav\" in df.columns else 1000000.0\n        today = datetime.now()\n        week_ago = today - pd.Timedelta(days=7)\n        df_week = df[df[date_col] >= week_ago]\n        last_row = df.iloc[-1]\n        last_nav = float(last_row.get(\"nav\", initial_nav))\n        first_week_row = df_week.iloc[0] if len(df_week) > 0 else df.iloc[0]\n        first_nav = float(first_week_row.get(\"nav\", initial_nav))\n        total_return = (last_nav / initial_nav - 1.0) * 100\n        week_return = (last_nav / first_nav - 1.0) * 100 if len(df_week) > 0 else 0.0\n        return {\n            \"latest_nav\": last_nav,\n            \"initial_nav\": initial_nav,\n            \"total_return_pct\": total_return,\n            \"week_return_pct\": week_return,\n            \"latest_date\": str(last_row.get(date_col, \"\"))[:10],\n            \"data_points\": len(df),\n        }\n    except Exception:\n        return None\n\n\ndef load_latest_account(profile_slug: str) -> dict | None:\n    json_path = REPORT_DIR / f\"paper_{profile_slug}_account_v1_latest.json\"\n    if not json_path.exists():\n        return None\n    try:\n        data = json.loads(json_path.read_text(encoding=\"utf-8\"))\n        return {\n            \"trade_date\": data.get(\"trade_date\") or data.get(\"date_tag\"),\n            \"date_tag\": data.get(\"date_tag\"),\n            \"nav\": data.get(\"nav\"),\n            \"total_return_pct\": data.get(\"total_return_pct\"),\n            \"day_pnl\": data.get(\"day_pnl\"),\n            \"drawdown_pct\": data.get(\"drawdown_pct\"),\n            \"position_count\": data.get(\"position_count\"),\n            \"today_trade_count\": data.get(\"today_trade_count\"),\n            \"today_buy_count\": data.get(\"today_buy_count\"),\n            \"today_sell_count\": data.get(\"today_sell_count\"),\n            \"source\": json_path.name,\n        }\n    except Exception:\n        return None\n\n\ndef load_cb_market_data() -> dict:\n"},{"oldText":"    lines.append(\"\")\n    lines.append(\"## 2. 模拟盘本周表现\")\n    for profile in [\"v4_3_aggressive\", \"aggressive\", \"balanced\", \"defensive\"]:\n        nav = load_paper_nav_csv(profile)\n        if nav:\n            lines.append(f\"- {profile}: 本周 {nav['week_return_pct']:+.2f}%, 累计 {nav['total_return_pct']:+.2f}%, 最新NAV {nav['latest_nav']:.4f} ({nav['latest_date']})\")\n        else:\n            lines.append(f\"- {profile}: 无数据\")\n","newText":"    lines.append(\"\")\n    lines.append(\"## 2A. 模拟盘研究窗口快照（基于 NAV 曲线，仅用于观察最近一周/研究窗口表现）\")\n    for profile in [\"v4_3_aggressive\", \"aggressive\", \"balanced\", \"defensive\"]:\n        nav = load_paper_nav_csv(profile)\n        if nav:\n            lines.append(f\"- {profile}: 本周 {nav['week_return_pct']:+.2f}%, 累计 {nav['total_return_pct']:+.2f}%, 最新NAV {nav['latest_nav']:.4f} ({nav['latest_date']})\")\n        else:\n            lines.append(f\"- {profile}: 无数据\")\n\n    lines.append(\"\")\n    lines.append(\"## 2B. 最新策略健康快照（基于 latest account JSON，作为当前状态主口径）\")\n    for profile in [\"v4_3_aggressive\", \"aggressive\", \"balanced\", \"defensive\"]:\n        account = load_latest_account(profile)\n        if account:\n            nav_value = account.get(\"nav\")\n            nav_text = f\"{float(nav_value):.2f}\" if nav_value is not None else \"?\"\n            ret_value = account.get(\"total_return_pct\")\n            ret_text = f\"{float(ret_value):+.2f}%\" if ret_value is not None else \"?\"\n            dd_value = account.get(\"drawdown_pct\")\n            dd_text = f\"{float(dd_value):+.2f}%\" if dd_value is not None else \"?\"\n            lines.append(\n                f\"- {profile}: 当前累计 {ret_text}, NAV {nav_text}, 回撤 {dd_text}, 持仓 {account.get('position_count', '?')} 只, \"\n                f\"当日买卖 {account.get('today_buy_count', '?')}/{account.get('today_sell_count', '?')} ({account.get('trade_date', '?')}, 来源 {account.get('source')})\"\n            )\n        else:\n            lines.append(f\"- {profile}: 无 latest account 数据\")\n\n    lines.append(\"\")\n    lines.append(\"口径纪律：\")\n    lines.append(\"- 2A 只能用于描述研究窗口/最近一周表现，不能直接当作当前风险证据。\")\n    lines.append(\"- 2B 才是当前策略健康状态的主口径；若 2A 与 2B 日期不一致，输出里必须显式写出‘日期错层’。\")\n"},{"oldText":"    lines.append(\"\")\n    lines.append(\"## 4. 任务\")\n    lines.append(\"根据以上数据，写出 3~5 条新的策略假设。\")\n    lines.append(\"格式要求：\")\n    lines.append(\"- 每条假设包含：假设描述、背后的数据支撑、建议的验证方法\")\n    lines.append(\"- 重点关注：最新窗口表现差的原因、模拟盘持续亏损的模式、现有参数的改进空间\")\n    lines.append(\"- 输出为 Markdown 格式，存入 research/reports/hypothesis/YYYYMMDD_hypotheses.md\")\n    lines.append(\"- 如有重大发现（如策略在某类行情下系统性失效），单独输出一条高优先级告警\")\n","newText":"    lines.append(\"\")\n    lines.append(\"## 4. 输出任务（必须按三层结构生成）\")\n    lines.append(\"先写《三层风险快照》，再写 3~5 条策略假设。\")\n    lines.append(\"\")\n    lines.append(\"### Layer 1. 市场环境快照\")\n    lines.append(\"- 只引用市场环境与研究窗口数据：Walk-Forward、市场温度、双低值、溢价率、平均价格、到期收益率\")\n    lines.append(\"- 回答：当前市场是否过热/过冷？是否进入对该策略不利的 regime？\")\n    lines.append(\"\")\n    lines.append(\"### Layer 2. 策略健康快照\")\n    lines.append(\"- 只引用 2B 的 latest account JSON 作为当前状态主口径\")\n    lines.append(\"- 必须写清 aggressive / balanced / defensive 的最新累计收益、NAV、持仓/交易状态\")\n    lines.append(\"- 若 2A 与 2B 日期不一致，必须显式写出：研究窗口日期 vs 当前账户日期\")\n    lines.append(\"\")\n    lines.append(\"### Layer 3. 假设与动作建议\")\n    lines.append(\"- 给出 3~5 条策略假设\")\n    lines.append(\"- 每条假设都要包含：假设描述、数据支撑、验证方法\")\n    lines.append(\"- 动作建议分成两类：研究动作 / 交易动作\")\n    lines.append(\"- 只有 Layer 1 与 Layer 2 同时支持、且日期一致或已显式说明错层时，才允许输出高优先级告警\")\n    lines.append(\"\")\n    lines.append(\"### 强约束\")\n    lines.append(\"- 禁止把旧快照累计收益写成当前策略表现\")\n    lines.append(\"- 禁止用研究窗口亏损直接推出当前账户亏损\")\n    lines.append(\"- 若证据只支持研究判断，不支持当前交易判断，明确写：‘这是研究预警，不是交易警报’\")\n    lines.append(\"- 输出为 Markdown 格式，存入 research/reports/hypothesis/YYYYMMDD_hypotheses.md\")\n    lines.append(\"- 可参考模板：research/reports/hypothesis/HYPOTHESIS_RISK_SNAPSHOT_TEMPLATE.md\")\n"}]},"partialJson":"{\"path\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/run_strategy_hypothesis_weekly.py\",\"edits\":[{\"oldText\":\"def load_paper_nav_csv(profile_slug: str) -> dict | None:\\n    csv_path = REPORT_DIR / f\\\"paper_{profile_slug}_nav_curve_v1.csv\\\"\\n    if not csv_path.exists():\\n        return None\\n    try:\\n        import pandas as pd\\n        df = pd.read_csv(csv_path)\\n        if \\\"date\\\" not in df.columns and \\\"trade_date\\\" not in df.columns:\\n            return None\\n        date_col = \\\"date\\\" if \\\"date\\\" in df.columns else \\\"trade_date\\\"\\n        df[date_col] = pd.to_datetime(df[date_col], errors=\\\"coerce\\\")\\n        df = df.dropna(subset=[date_col]).sort_values(date_col)\\n        if len(df) < 2:\\n            return None\\n        # NAV 从 initial_cash（1000000.0）开始，计算相对收益率\\n        initial_nav = float(df.iloc[0][\\\"nav\\\"]) if \\\"nav\\\" in df.columns else 1000000.0\\n        today = datetime.now()\\n        week_ago = today - pd.Timedelta(days=7)\\n        df_week = df[df[date_col] >= week_ago]\\n        last_row = df.iloc[-1]\\n        last_nav = float(last_row.get(\\\"nav\\\", initial_nav))\\n        first_week_row = df_week.iloc[0] if len(df_week) > 0 else df.iloc[0]\\n        first_nav = float(first_week_row.get(\\\"nav\\\", initial_nav))\\n        total_return = (last_nav / initial_nav - 1.0) * 100\\n        week_return = (last_nav / first_nav - 1.0) * 100 if len(df_week) > 0 else 0.0\\n        return {\\n            \\\"latest_nav\\\": last_nav,\\n            \\\"initial_nav\\\": initial_nav,\\n            \\\"total_return_pct\\\": total_return,\\n            \\\"week_return_pct\\\": week_return,\\n            \\\"latest_date\\\": str(last_row.get(date_col, \\\"\\\"))[:10],\\n            \\\"data_points\\\": len(df),\\n        }\\n    except Exception:\\n        return None\\n\\n\\ndef load_cb_market_data() -> dict:\\n\",\"newText\":\"def load_paper_nav_csv(profile_slug: str) -> dict | None:\\n    csv_path = REPORT_DIR / f\\\"paper_{profile_slug}_nav_curve_v1.csv\\\"\\n    if not csv_path.exists():\\n        return None\\n    try:\\n        import pandas as pd\\n        df = pd.read_csv(csv_path)\\n        if \\\"date\\\" not in df.columns and \\\"trade_date\\\" not in df.columns:\\n            return None\\n        date_col = \\\"date\\\" if \\\"date\\\" in df.columns else \\\"trade_date\\\"\\n        df[date_col] = pd.to_datetime(df[date_col], errors=\\\"coerce\\\")\\n        df = df.dropna(subset=[date_col]).sort_values(date_col)\\n        if len(df) < 2:\\n            return None\\n        # NAV 从 initial_cash（1000000.0）开始，计算相对收益率\\n        initial_nav = float(df.iloc[0][\\\"nav\\\"]) if \\\"nav\\\" in df.columns else 1000000.0\\n        today = datetime.now()\\n        week_ago = today - pd.Timedelta(days=7)\\n        df_week = df[df[date_col] >= week_ago]\\n        last_row = df.iloc[-1]\\n        last_nav = float(last_row.get(\\\"nav\\\", initial_nav))\\n        first_week_row = df_week.iloc[0] if len(df_week) > 0 else df.iloc[0]\\n        first_nav = float(first_week_row.get(\\\"nav\\\", initial_nav))\\n        total_return = (last_nav / initial_nav - 1.0) * 100\\n        week_return = (last_nav / first_nav - 1.0) * 100 if len(df_week) > 0 else 0.0\\n        return {\\n            \\\"latest_nav\\\": last_nav,\\n            \\\"initial_nav\\\": initial_nav,\\n            \\\"total_return_pct\\\": total_return,\\n            \\\"week_return_pct\\\": week_return,\\n            \\\"latest_date\\\": str(last_row.get(date_col, \\\"\\\"))[:10],\\n            \\\"data_points\\\": len(df),\\n        }\\n    except Exception:\\n        return None\\n\\n\\ndef load_latest_account(profile_slug: str) -> dict | None:\\n    json_path = REPORT_DIR / f\\\"paper_{profile_slug}_account_v1_latest.json\\\"\\n    if not json_path.exists():\\n        return None\\n    try:\\n        data = json.loads(json_path.read_text(encoding=\\\"utf-8\\\"))\\n        return {\\n            \\\"trade_date\\\": data.get(\\\"trade_date\\\") or data.get(\\\"date_tag\\\"),\\n            \\\"date_tag\\\": data.get(\\\"date_tag\\\"),\\n            \\\"nav\\\": data.get(\\\"nav\\\"),\\n            \\\"total_return_pct\\\": data.get(\\\"total_return_pct\\\"),\\n            \\\"day_pnl\\\": data.get(\\\"day_pnl\\\"),\\n            \\\"drawdown_pct\\\": data.get(\\\"drawdown_pct\\\"),\\n            \\\"position_count\\\": data.get(\\\"position_count\\\"),\\n            \\\"today_trade_count\\\": data.get(\\\"today_trade_count\\\"),\\n            \\\"today_buy_count\\\": data.get(\\\"today_buy_count\\\"),\\n            \\\"today_sell_count\\\": data.get(\\\"today_sell_count\\\"),\\n            \\\"source\\\": json_path.name,\\n        }\\n    except Exception:\\n        return None\\n\\n\\ndef load_cb_market_data() -> dict:\\n\"},{\"oldText\":\"    lines.append(\\\"\\\")\\n    lines.append(\\\"## 2. 模拟盘本周表现\\\")\\n    for profile in [\\\"v4_3_aggressive\\\", \\\"aggressive\\\", \\\"balanced\\\", \\\"defensive\\\"]:\\n        nav = load_paper_nav_csv(profile)\\n        if nav:\\n            lines.append(f\\\"- {profile}: 本周 {nav['week_return_pct']:+.2f}%, 累计 {nav['total_return_pct']:+.2f}%, 最新NAV {nav['latest_nav']:.4f} ({nav['latest_date']})\\\")\\n        else:\\n            lines.append(f\\\"- {profile}: 无数据\\\")\\n\",\"newText\":\"    lines.append(\\\"\\\")\\n    lines.append(\\\"## 2A. 模拟盘研究窗口快照（基于 NAV 曲线，仅用于观察最近一周/研究窗口表现）\\\")\\n    for profile in [\\\"v4_3_aggressive\\\", \\\"aggressive\\\", \\\"balanced\\\", \\\"defensive\\\"]:\\n        nav = load_paper_nav_csv(profile)\\n        if nav:\\n            lines.append(f\\\"- {profile}: 本周 {nav['week_return_pct']:+.2f}%, 累计 {nav['total_return_pct']:+.2f}%, 最新NAV {nav['latest_nav']:.4f} ({nav['latest_date']})\\\")\\n        else:\\n            lines.append(f\\\"- {profile}: 无数据\\\")\\n\\n    lines.append(\\\"\\\")\\n    lines.append(\\\"## 2B. 最新策略健康快照（基于 latest account JSON，作为当前状态主口径）\\\")\\n    for profile in [\\\"v4_3_aggressive\\\", \\\"aggressive\\\", \\\"balanced\\\", \\\"defensive\\\"]:\\n        account = load_latest_account(profile)\\n        if account:\\n            nav_value = account.get(\\\"nav\\\")\\n            nav_text = f\\\"{float(nav_value):.2f}\\\" if nav_value is not None else \\\"?\\\"\\n            ret_value = account.get(\\\"total_return_pct\\\")\\n            ret_text = f\\\"{float(ret_value):+.2f}%\\\" if ret_value is not None else \\\"?\\\"\\n            dd_value = account.get(\\\"drawdown_pct\\\")\\n            dd_text = f\\\"{float(dd_value):+.2f}%\\\" if dd_value is not None else \\\"?\\\"\\n            lines.append(\\n                f\\\"- {profile}: 当前累计 {ret_text}, NAV {nav_text}, 回撤 {dd_text}, 持仓 {account.get('position_count', '?')} 只, \\\"\\n                f\\\"当日买卖 {account.get('today_buy_count', '?')}/{account.get('today_sell_count', '?')} ({account.get('trade_date', '?')}, 来源 {account.get('source')})\\\"\\n            )\\n        else:\\n            lines.append(f\\\"- {profile}: 无 latest account 数据\\\")\\n\\n    lines.append(\\\"\\\")\\n    lines.append(\\\"口径纪律：\\\")\\n    lines.append(\\\"- 2A 只能用于描述研究窗口/最近一周表现，不能直接当作当前风险证据。\\\")\\n    lines.append(\\\"- 2B 才是当前策略健康状态的主口径；若 2A 与 2B 日期不一致，输出里必须显式写出‘日期错层’。\\\")\\n\"},{\"oldText\":\"    lines.append(\\\"\\\")\\n    lines.append(\\\"## 4. 任务\\\")\\n    lines.append(\\\"根据以上数据，写出 3~5 条新的策略假设。\\\")\\n    lines.append(\\\"格式要求：\\\")\\n    lines.append(\\\"- 每条假设包含：假设描述、背后的数据支撑、建议的验证方法\\\")\\n    lines.append(\\\"- 重点关注：最新窗口表现差的原因、模拟盘持续亏损的模式、现有参数的改进空间\\\")\\n    lines.append(\\\"- 输出为 Markdown 格式，存入 research/reports/hypothesis/YYYYMMDD_hypotheses.md\\\")\\n    lines.append(\\\"- 如有重大发现（如策略在某类行情下系统性失效），单独输出一条高优先级告警\\\")\\n\",\"newText\":\"    lines.append(\\\"\\\")\\n    lines.append(\\\"## 4. 输出任务（必须按三层结构生成）\\\")\\n    lines.append(\\\"先写《三层风险快照》，再写 3~5 条策略假设。\\\")\\n    lines.append(\\\"\\\")\\n    lines.append(\\\"### Layer 1. 市场环境快照\\\")\\n    lines.append(\\\"- 只引用市场环境与研究窗口数据：Walk-Forward、市场温度、双低值、溢价率、平均价格、到期收益率\\\")\\n    lines.append(\\\"- 回答：当前市场是否过热/过冷？是否进入对该策略不利的 regime？\\\")\\n    lines.append(\\\"\\\")\\n    lines.append(\\\"### Layer 2. 策略健康快照\\\")\\n    lines.append(\\\"- 只引用 2B 的 latest account JSON 作为当前状态主口径\\\")\\n    lines.append(\\\"- 必须写清 aggressive / balanced / defensive 的最新累计收益、NAV、持仓/交易状态\\\")\\n    lines.append(\\\"- 若 2A 与 2B 日期不一致，必须显式写出：研究窗口日期 vs 当前账户日期\\\")\\n    lines.append(\\\"\\\")\\n    lines.append(\\\"### Layer 3. 假设与动作建议\\\")\\n    lines.append(\\\"- 给出 3~5 条策略假设\\\")\\n    lines.append(\\\"- 每条假设都要包含：假设描述、数据支撑、验证方法\\\")\\n    lines.append(\\\"- 动作建议分成两类：研究动作 / 交易动作\\\")\\n    lines.append(\\\"- 只有 Layer 1 与 Layer 2 同时支持、且日期一致或已显式说明错层时，才允许输出高优先级告警\\\")\\n    lines.append(\\\"\\\")\\n    lines.append(\\\"### 强约束\\\")\\n    lines.append(\\\"- 禁止把旧快照累计收益写成当前策略表现\\\")\\n    lines.append(\\\"- 禁止用研究窗口亏损直接推出当前账户亏损\\\")\\n    lines.append(\\\"- 若证据只支持研究判断，不支持当前交易判断，明确写：‘这是研究预警，不是交易警报’\\\")\\n    lines.append(\\\"- 输出为 Markdown 格式，存入 research/reports/hypothesis/YYYYMMDD_hypotheses.md\\\")\\n    lines.append(\\\"- 可参考模板：research/reports/hypothesis/HYPOTHESIS_RISK_SNAPSHOT_TEMPLATE.md\\\")\\n\"}]}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"beecode","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":77248,"output":4804,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":82052,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776504800716,"responseId":"resp_0fad9e409c19087f0169e34fe20704819abf6ec5819bc67694"}}
