不稳，导致后续渲染链路挂掉\n\n我已经重新生成了 aggressive 的最新 dashboard，验证过：\n- `tradeTable` 不再是空 `<tbody>`\n- `const allTrades` 里也不再有裸 `NaN`\n\n提交也打了：\n- `cc42f8a4d` — `Fix blank trade log layer fallback rendering`\n\n这次我顺手刷新了：\n- `paper_aggressive_trading_dashboard_latest.html`\n- `paper_aggressive_trading_dashboard_20260417.html`\n\n如果你要，我下一步可以把 **balanced / defensive / v4_3** 这几个 latest dashboard 也一起重刷一遍。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0fad9e409c19087f0169e3a198e4ac819a88c6f87887ac88ca\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"beecode","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":140619,"output":387,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":141006,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776525714171,"responseId":"resp_0fad9e409c19087f0169e3a194e2a0819a9517b00a75aaa7e6"}}
