{"type":"message","id":"32f0e36c","parentId":"92780e95","timestamp":"2026-04-18T16:07:05.058Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Analyzing stock strategy**\n\nI'm thinking about a rebound or mean-reversion bet after a pullback, rather than following a stable trend leader. If the stock is currently above 85-90, I might need a volume breakout or to wait for a pullback near support. If it dips below 80, I question its strength. I see local support around 85 to 80, and losing 80 could mean structural issues. It’s important to avoid speculation and reference costs accurately. \n\nI should summarize my conclusions clearly, including limitations of the analysis based on local data.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_0fad9e409c19087f0169e3abfee3d8819a97da38dc7744073b\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp46wQ0BynwIhct-kRO6t2ZQaGOzI605JfMlM5N1_Ac97iEJl3hoKtilRcUXTGo95_VZGI2JC7_taUtoJUQ4MlcDiM1Qiy4LJsmNkbPjANlXmKn_6rDVWFMrd1GUCPnuUZCZrsh0r31tudb0lufAqYgj6Woim0kjrybLnfFll_83xiKEXkZ0JfBLana9eYUw9MC7CdYhAOBUYPHLXTZvVj9-SuI20kvRRdQ1hiLZv7Wwrin6aY5D20VdMBMnrmsVkvryLRksgq-bcUcX8rNzqj6afU2J2BgJEWZBtDEJZ71JNQuM0cRSsmi132uD29812RGQbkCx6vlMgNUlVi5LkcKh_q9dzft09DbrZB5IkdRRBqrUZFdV5YHwPR6jMmVTeSxd4zf7A9W19wPauN9lFY8wbhb8AfhFihSjKl0RH-wC8E4O1FYUeSXTugbRgBz8LvIdteaouyPtHe1Wmcyhap_v6i7iQvAnpWu3O4sLnBpwL-1s5czE9_-oOsTRo0iS1GMzybNrTKVoG0_NPWRo0EEqIIorBUl4EKt-3YqqKhUMVAbtNE1Ydu7C8Y6OC3Z3w09l1iMa9cKe1nb13fVpgyfx7u3pkmMTjtYtp-LI2Cw2JweGr6YCnHs5ZJwbARnOyWuZkMHCcXtaircJNTvHftBl46jUbV63o8Mvpg5sjQ9RSOSeYBQ3xXZhcEFVHinGy3KNC0wzAfiUhRzr4zAjsYAZABqAMtweudvXq1KpMVcK9-fJ0Oo6XeKMvfLGZC4j4VYT4TaMKo8k2srQ21oPF1h2U4phTpvS6EgL7Qb8hLXUcUOuhZYbbVXFONqlepoOF5ZFJTmmSSkICkfpc70j_X-zBH4fWugUVG0m1M1Mmj3G6dROP8KS0RlqfJeOiSCcTJmEZ6-JAMEETLTunZmGDgzLHlri7npt4PJlJXVA4z9l0E3YMROAFvbzKzzz7qnXvMSNsUU5SCJhEi5ydbg5LBi2XgGTiKpYo1lT3vapgInzAIPELLgeP3IwLeSR91SdR6qnh_sYy-1U1CcBkZOiubL_03IFqTt7ZE7r3L2-OCdUFR_tIcg5DiuQlgWXjMzHaWHtUWP2Yw_QxmxjwXdscmXUAfrfUN26JUT4cmyn3qhvrTz