{"type":"message","id":"2686d796","parentId":"3af797a5","timestamp":"2026-04-18T16:09:48.870Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_Q1xKNtfv5y299KDGhYS9aPCf|fc_0fad9e409c19087f0169e3accb1184819aac7463a14f5f1a92","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"﻿trade_date,ts_code,action,target_value,target_weight,target_qty,ref_price,strategy_id,score,risk_adjustment,risk_status,exit_type,exit_reason,reduce_score,reduce_rank_reason,reason,source_signal_file,generated_at,approved,ai_stock_name,ai_operation_advice,ai_trend_prediction,ai_sentiment_score,ai_decision,ai_budget_scale,ai_score_scale,ai_gate_reason,ai_analysis_status,ai_analysis_time,ai_analysis_summary,ai_risk_warning,ai_stop_loss,ai_take_profit,ai_no_position_advice,ai_has_position_advice,ai_rsi14,ai_rsi_signal,ai_realtime_source,ai_realtime_price,ai_realtime_change_pct,ai_realtime_confirmed\n2026-04-15,002119.SZ,BUY,56144.236387096775,0.0516129032258064,,,smallcap_chip_v4_2b,0.847041,none|scale_total_exposure,normal,,,,,auto_live_v4_2b_fundamental_guard,/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/paper_aggressive_merged_signals_profiled_20260415.csv,2026-04-16T21:13:27.442028+08:00,True,康强电子,买入,看多,64,pass,1.0,1.0,股票分析建议=买入,live,2026-04-16T21:34:35.650383,康强电子技术面呈现明确的多头排列格局，MA5、MA10、MA20依次向上发散，趋势转强。今日放量上涨，但当前价格偏离MA5约3.47%，处于‘可小仓介入’但需警惕追高的警戒区间。基本面有2025年业绩同比增长40%的利好支撑，但动态市盈率高达72倍，估值压力显著。综合判断，趋势向好但短期追高风险与估值压力并存，适合轻仓、分批、设好止损的试探性操作。,高估值（PE 72.76）是核心风险，股价短期涨幅已偏离均线，存在技术性回调压力。A股T+1交易制度下，当日买入无法卖出，需注意隔夜风险。,,,空仓者建议：可在股价回踩MA5（21.82元）附近时，轻仓（1-2成）试探性买入。,持仓者建议：可继续持有，若股价继续上涨且乖离率扩大至5%以上，可考虑部分减仓锁定利润。,,,tushare,22.58,4.01,True\n2026-04-15,002272.SZ,BUY,56144.236387096775,0.0516129032258064,,,smallcap_chip_v4_2b,0.811515,none|scale_total_exposure,normal,,,,,auto_live_v4_2b_fundamental_guard,/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/paper_aggressive_merged_signals_profiled_20260415.csv,2026-04-16T21:13:2