yE0sw6qXvTX2TDL--g-R_46N796UHqVOpGrhdQJu-Zvd6UEfBq7nOd2woagh68CAUmUrHUQtrq7JSavXrpQtr4cCY-HlEdmfNbUJ-HmPwh7jtIGP2Tf2_eawJfKmkiHvmyxuUgraED86XQGzxcXH1XzT3Hzy7QVA5lFvsDq1U57i55ms94qCNKxATKdh-48MYGn_TjqJ4PZTubQ9naP0YREZbXuX716nzkWSPCiACIslsEYulxCKvY9BdFE26-AmXvNnF3xWZx5yZibUEFweCgru514WIl_Vx_w==\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Updating user on progress**\\n\\nI need to respond to the user about \\\"继续\\\" with a concise update, mentioning what I've done so far and that I'm continuing to patch other scripts still using a_stock_history. It seems like the user wants to move forward after my earlier comment about fixing an issue. I should acknowledge the continuation of the process, point out that many research scripts still use a_stock_history for backtests, and maybe mention commit hashes to keep it brief.\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 继续了，刚又往前推了一层。\n\n这次我补的是**分析展示链路**，不只是补价脚本：\n\n1. **`position_explainer` 默认优先读 enriched 持仓**\n   - 现在会优先吃  \n     `selected_real_positions_YYYYMMDD_enriched.csv`\n   - 不再默认回到原始持仓 CSV\n\n2. **把价格新鲜度一路带到报告里**\n   - 新增并透传：\n     - `price_source`\n     - `price_timestamp`\n     - `price_is_stale`\n   - `position_explainer` 的 markdown 会直接显示  \n     **价格来源 / FRESH or STALE / 时间**\n\n3. **`multi_perspective_merger` 也带价格口径**\n   - 综合日报里，持仓项现在会显示价格来源和新鲜度\n   - 不再只给一个裸价格\n\n4. **`generate_single_stock_lens.py` 也改了**\n   - 真实持仓部分现在优先读 enriched 文件\n   - 会显示：\n     - 当前价\n     - 当日涨跌\n     - 价格口径（source / fresh-stale / timestamp）\n\n5. **已经过最小验证**\n   - 编译通过\n   - `position_explainer` 默认解析到的 holdings 路径，已经是  \n     `selected_real_positions_20260415_enriched.csv`\n\n这次提交是：\n- `20077846a`\n- `Propagate quote freshness through overlays`\n\n现在至少**补价链路、持仓解释、综合研判、单票 lens** 这几条用户可见链路，已经开始讲清楚“这价格是不是新鲜的”。\n\n如果你要，我下一步继续清：\n**把还在用户口径里直接吃 `a_stock_history.csv` 的单票分析/选股报告脚本也逐个改掉。**","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0fad9e409c19087f0169e3b3f34070819a88f11f09fffcc883\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"beecode","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":55552,"output":510,"cacheRead":205952,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":262014,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776530408155,"responseId":"resp_0fad9e409c19087f0169e3b3ea6e38819aa919d5a086f6d2c0"}}
