{"type":"message","id":"b8c5e882","parentId":"df3e4a4a","timestamp":"2026-04-18T16:47:19.068Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Evaluating candidate generation edits**\n\nI need to focus on editing the candidate generation summary. It could really benefit from including some real-time freshness metadata, like the current market trade date and the lag days. I might consider adding fields for real-time mode requested or used, along with the real-time injected count. Additionally, incorporating a price freshness indicator, such as FRESH or STALE, could help. I should also check how prepare_live_signal_tickets interacts with the auto_candidate_summary.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_0fad9e409c19087f0169e3b58b8458819a93b4cac1bcfb34e1\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp47WP1mr30iGlAcVICQ3g1vFZnjbPjOF4yCeUAfLSx_Agye-WHq5zAI0iDsAaKxD-lqCkUOkj_9G-d-ilCM21L4PSUtil_1o-pa6Vte-8tRZYOS1n8hch7BcEOFgtkD5sBXghOYPLhAm4H7pmSIL0d4FrGOjE5iE35ITxHGhoKTi6eaolGF2iSvwhonm4DYBQqSYNmrv51BS0mAUbZ-Tqo7ip0QSkNO3H03q81XZhz5BzfC6HWcGhZmD3CZv8FRhsBn08f270S4IxZ1yHUshmcsDuu5qhUAr9T_CInMCAl3qe_QHRsvq9EbSi-LZTt5D3BBftt4BXdQpDbicPzekJOrSQkWKGRt1kcA4n4lF1V62lpuEiUtuXqGzs6cMXicNkhZDjAW02iR8lLkYEjFNfIbQ3UoP7jVxmasBVMN_Ll2tn1aXoeD4HHYbM8xVD6VkLdlGEXIVfaRQVyAYt7PIfCo7bNti0sRAmpOveVIX-40RZ47GUF0W2VxAaY2jQrne56NGkic1odG52_wRbFDJsN1cAfF6_DuPAMwU9OA-8_TxKfA5iujQWHwSafFZdJhCTMCsA-e7DA_9_zs0esG2dBz79US059MQXJz8hPUkeEIlHR4w-QZag-3t9NQu3c7u_HqCDC_uqefTkdMTK8-XLRtDX3yTaoSC1Si_qhn9KplaYhS_6OKRPHLuhTR4xiE3WVWkt8xJY4HQWrSSXgO9NDQpviXAjOAnOTh7BEv2Fn8mUVDMV3IKWRVhX1a5d4xpiGQU9tPZXkwORAFpYuq3HChKpAxIRJRoFcU2PEhfvF1L-AZv9FvP5ki-6RJSpe7zSdOCYfHnMF_xbQs8VZSrbVa_06HOUH5-R_MW8vVelq_CtfaOAuKP4KtEj-zArNiTkcnuLwn2tY33l-irXd1EkO9AsUOkPO8fc58ndkEv9At1QQ2ktDA7HxxnU7Cv8Ggh1crkWS4rZOqNlSMuzv-v5dcvcu_GruF96teYM6iHgqOLyA-jwXnUbWoGQghKcaJinmrrYSAUAInqs3Wu3KFYZ52AlTa2ZXOIxmc-yS2UOuvPVkXNlZbH1FB8xB_vduVQ4fMk0x0HGWmHHCOAUiS1hfRF04D95Q8IIcFlzlKuOzbTjZ0UoMpBK5jPXYvhQ_IyLIo2DKgX