的：**\n1. **信号桥 → 执行单 tickets**\n   - `stock_analysis_decision_bridge.py`\n   - `prepare_live_signal_tickets.py`\n   - 现在会显式带：\n     - `ai_realtime_freshness`\n     - `source_price_mode`\n   - 而且 tickets 不会再把**未确认的 ai_realtime_price**直接当下单参考价  \n     只有确认 fresh 才优先用，否则回退到别的参考价/历史 close\n\n2. **候选生成摘要**\n   - `generate_live_smallcap_candidates.py`\n   - summary 现在明确写：\n     - `price_mode`\n     - `price_freshness`\n     - `realtime_requested`\n     - `realtime_attempted`\n     - `realtime_injected_count`\n     - `realtime_source`\n   - `top_preview` 也带上了：\n     - `close`\n     - `source_trade_date`\n\n**我刚重跑验证过：**\n- `live_smallcap_candidate_generation_20260417.json`\n- 里面已经是：\n  - `price_mode = realtime_injected`\n  - `price_freshness = FRESH`\n  - `realtime_injected_count = 300`\n  - `realtime_source = tencent`\n\n**提交：**\n- `bb7213209` — `Track quote freshness in live ticket pipeline`\n- `06570d6ef` — `Annotate candidate generation with price freshness`\n\n**当前已修到的链路：**\n- 持仓补价\n- 持仓解释 overlay\n- 综合研判 merger\n- 单票 lens\n- 今日策略总览\n- 候选生成摘要\n- 执行单 / live tickets\n\n**还在继续扫的剩余问题：**\n- 一个外部依赖链里的**股票名补全/旧 Tushare & pytdx fallback 噪音报错**\n- 这不直接影响价格 freshness，但会污染日志，我下一轮继续把它清掉。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0fad9e409c19087f0169e3b9fe7a50819a999f47f1c117a3b4\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"beecode","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":96215,"output":706,"cacheRead":232704,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":329625,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776531950976,"responseId":"resp_0fad9e409c19087f0169e3b9f1db44819a8a11e126d829f183"}}
